<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Browze" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Browze,</orth> to nibble<cit><quote>: --ing of ivy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.3.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 3, 69</bibl></cit> (cf. <emph>of</emph>). <cit><quote>the barks of trees thou --dst,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 1.4.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 4, 66</bibl></cit>.<lb />Intr.: <cit><quote>there is cold meat i' the cave; we'll b. on that,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.6.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 6, 38</bibl></cit>.

